reviews.text: Despite the long travel time, I have been coming to this clinic for over 15 years for aesthetic treatments. The staff are always friendly and helpful. Dr. Janet is exceptionally warm and professional. she always recommends treatments that are best suited to my needs.

I have been seeing Dr Janet for the past 20years. A professional, caring doctor whom I can trust. Otherwise, I would have stopped seeing her long ago. Attentive and listens patiently. Gives good advice. Adopts a Holistic approach to treatment. Her team of receptionist are efficient. Knows their patients well. Friendly and approachable.

I have been visiting the clinic for years and this has been our family preferred doctor. Dr Janet has always been the best. She would always listens to our medical conditions and gives positive advises with the correct prescriptions.
The clinic assistants are all very helpful and friendly.
A good place to get treatment. Doctor will give a thorough check up. Just be prepared to wait a little longer by ut worth the wait.

Dr Janet Lee is a great family doctor with many years of experience and up to date medical knowledge. She is always warm and gives good medical explanation and advice. She also does not over prescribe .Her staff members are also efficient and speedy in dispensing medications with clear explanations. Highly recommended clinic!
